{"id": "test-02763", "text": "ALPINE SKIING-OFFICIALS HOPE TO SALVAGE WORLD CUP WEEKEND.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 40, "end": 49, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "WORLD CUP"}]}
{"id": "test-02764", "text": "WHISTLER, British Columbia 1996-12-06", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 8, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "WHISTLER"}, {"start": 10, "end": 26, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "British Columbia"}]}
{"id": "test-02765", "text": "World Cup ski officials hope to be able to get in at least one men's downhill training run on Saturday in an effort to salvage the weekend racing programme.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "World Cup"}]}
{"id": "test-02766", "text": "For the third consecutive day, Friday's scheduled training runs were cancelled due to heavy wet snow and fog on Whistler Mountain, leaving the scheduled World Cup events in jeopardy.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 112, "end": 129, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Whistler Mountain"}, {"start": 153, "end": 162, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "World Cup"}]}
{"id": "test-02767", "text": "Rules call for at least one training run to be completed before a World Cup downhill race can be staged.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 66, "end": 75, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "World Cup"}]}
{"id": "test-02768", "text": "Organisers hope to get that run in on Saturday morning, conditions permitting, and stage the race later in the day or on Sunday.", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-02769", "text": "\"There was no possibility today to make a training run, \"said Bernd Zobel, the Canadian men's national coach, citing too much new snow and poor visibility.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 62, "end": 73, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bernd Zobel"}, {"start": 79, "end": 87, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Canadian"}]}
{"id": "test-02770", "text": "If organisers are forced to run the downhill on Sunday, the super-giant slalom originally scheduled for Sunday would likely be abandoned.", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-02771", "text": "SOCCER - LEADING SCOTTISH PREMIER DIVISION SCORERS.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 17, "end": 42, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "SCOTTISH PREMIER DIVISION"}]}
